{
  "message": "test(fuzz): add 12 corpus seeds for shape_inference_engine\n\nStructured seeds targeting shape inference for key primitives:\n- add_2d_f32: binary Add with matching 2D F32 tensors\n- reduce_sum_axis0: ReduceSum with axis specification\n- reshape_3d_to_2d: Reshape from 3D to 2D\n- slice_2d: Slice on 2D tensor\n- transpose_3d: Transpose with axis reversal\n- broadcast_in_dim: BroadcastInDim from 1D to 2D\n- concat_axis0: Concatenate along axis 0\n- squeeze_dim1: Squeeze size-1 dimension\n- expand_dims: ExpandDims at axis 1\n- dot_matmul: Matrix multiplication\n- pad_2d: 2D padding\n- rev_axis1: Reverse along axis 1\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
